... I had the pleasure of being in the Guide Program in Beta through the first year or so and even was involved in helping update the Policy and Proceedure manual used by guides (you can blame me, in part, for the play nice policy &lt;evil grin&gt;). [Note: I left long time ago so no conflict of interest here <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ]<br>
